description:
PRE-ORDER DANNY'S NEW BOOK HERE: http://smarturl.it/unremember


Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured a San Diego trip, Sutton's foot troubles, and some mating sea creatures. Danny also talks a bit about his new book, How Do I Un-Remember This?: Unfortunately True Stories out March 8. 2022 (pre-order hardcover now, audiobook. e-book, and live event details coming soon) and a very important social media post from former VPR stars.


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
